com.amazonaws.services.stepfunctions.builder.states

Class TaskState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.stepfunctions.builder.states.TransitionState
      • com.amazonaws.services.stepfunctions.builder.states.TaskState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    State

    public final class TaskState
extends TransitionState
    The Task State causes the interpreter to execute the work identified by the state’s “Resource” field.

    Currently allowed resources include Lambda functions and States activities.

    See Also:
    https://states-language.net/spec.html#task-state
